\begin{aligned} f : &\mathbb{R}^{n} \to \mathbb{R} \\ &X \mapsto \bigg[ M \, (V + X) \bigg] \cdot \bigg[ E + \alpha X \bigg] \end{aligned}
\forall X \;,\; f(X) \geq 0 \;\; \Longrightarrow \;\; E = \alpha V
